'''''The Clone Wars Sourcebook''''' was a planned sourcebook for the [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]] from [[Wizards of the Coast]], written in [[2003]] by [[Daniel Wallace]] and [[J.D. Wiker]]. However, with Wizards' shift in focus to the [[Star Wars Miniatures]] game, the sourcebook was ultimately canceled. As it was to be released before the [[Star Wars Legends|Expanded Universe]] coverage of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] had ended, it would also not have contained information on important stories such as ''[[Labyrinth of Evil]]'' or [[Star Wars: Clone Wars Volume Two|''Star Wars: Clone Wars'' Volume Two]]. Much of the cut material was later reincorporated into ''[[The New Essential Chronology]]'', also by Dan Wallace.

